<div id="review_2445420345" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2445420345" />
    <a title="Chrissie" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/632247-chrissie"><img alt="Chrissie" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1321799585p2/632247.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2445420345?book_show_action=true">Jul 04, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Chrissie" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Chrissie" href="/user/show/632247-chrissie">Chrissie</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="did not like it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">did not like it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/632247-chrissie?shelf=returned">returned</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/632247-chrissie?shelf=poetry">poetry</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/632247-chrissie?shelf=2018-read">2018-read</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/632247-chrissie?shelf=audible-uk">audible-uk</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/632247-chrissie?shelf=kids">kids</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2445420345" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14395556292172640288">This book failed me totally. <br/><br/>It is a collection of poems. The poems have nothing to do with Christopher Robin, Winnie-the-Pooh, Piglet, Eeyore, Tiger, Owl, Kanga and Baby Roo. I do not think the poems will appeal to a child and they did not appeal to me, an adult. Skip this. <br/><br/>It is is not made magical even by the Peter Dennis&apos; excellent audiobook narration.<br/><br/>****************<br/>*<a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/99107.Winnie_the_Pooh__Winnie_the_Pooh___1_' title='Winnie-the-Pooh (Winnie-the-Pooh, #1) by A.A. Milne' rel='nofollow noopener'>Winnie-the-Pooh</a> 5 stars<br/>*<a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/776407.The_House_at_Pooh_Corner__Winnie_the_Pooh___2_' title='The House at Pooh Corner (Winnie-the-Pooh, #2) by A.A. Milne' rel='nofollow noopener'>The House at Pooh Corner</a> 4 stars<br/>*<a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/821003.When_We_Were_Very_Young__Winnie_the_Pooh___3_' title='When We Were Very Young (Winnie-the-Pooh, #3) by A.A. Milne' rel='nofollow noopener'>When We Were Very Young</a> 1 star</span>
  <span id="freeText14395556292172640288" style="display:none">This book failed me totally. <br /><br />It is a collection of poems. The poems have nothing to do with Christopher Robin, Winnie-the-Pooh, Piglet, Eeyore, Tiger, Owl, Kanga and Baby Roo. I do not think the poems will appeal to a child and they did not appeal to me, an adult. Skip this. <br /><br />It is is not made magical even by the Peter Dennis' excellent audiobook narration.<br /><br />****************<br />*<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/99107.Winnie_the_Pooh__Winnie_the_Pooh___1_" title="Winnie-the-Pooh (Winnie-the-Pooh, #1) by A.A. Milne" rel="nofollow noopener">Winnie-the-Pooh</a> 5 stars<br />*<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/776407.The_House_at_Pooh_Corner__Winnie_the_Pooh___2_" title="The House at Pooh Corner (Winnie-the-Pooh, #2) by A.A. Milne" rel="nofollow noopener">The House at Pooh Corner</a> 4 stars<br />*<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/821003.When_We_Were_Very_Young__Winnie_the_Pooh___3_" title="When We Were Very Young (Winnie-the-Pooh, #3) by A.A. Milne" rel="nofollow noopener">When We Were Very Young</a> 1 star</span>
