      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/3355608-when-we-were-very-young">Quotes from When We Were Very...</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;She turned to the sunlight<br />    And shook her yellow head,<br />And whispered to her neighbor:<br />    "Winter is dead.&rdquo;</span>
